    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſi/ wiꞥſch nah̄s aug-\nham/ un ſkreêg ahtri ka' Ehrgeiſis/ un iſplattihſ ſawus Spahr-\nuſ pahr Bozru. Un ta Sirds\no Warrenu no Gedoma buhs\nai Deenâ ka' ta Sirds weenas\nSeewas/ kaſ Behrnu-Sahpes\neefsch."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Prett Damasku. Gemate\nin Arpads faunahs/ tapehz ka\nee niſnu Slawu irr dſirdejſchi/\nee irr bailigi/ Juhr-Mallâ irr\nSkummitba/ ka duſſeht ne warr."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Damaskus irr nogurris/\nas irr greesees behgt/ Drebbe-\nchana irr to tagrahbufi/ Baaliba\nn Sahpes irr tohs fanehmu-\nchas/ ka weenu Seewu/ kaſ\nfeunde."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka? Wojwiꞥſch nu'ne irr\nitſtahts/ tas flawehts Pils-\nahts? Tas Pilsfahts mannas\nBreezibas."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz krittihs winna\nJaunekti us winna Gelahm/ un\nwiſſi Karra-Wihri taps tai Dee-\nâ iſdeldeti/ fakka tas KUNGS\nRebaot:"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es eededsinaſchu ug-\njuni eekſch Damaskus Muhra/\nin tas noribs BenAdada ſtat-\ntus Nammus."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Prett Keedaru/ un tahm\nWalsſibahm no Azora/ fo Ne-\nukadRezars tas Rehninsch no\nBabeles ſawe/ fakka tas KUNGS\nâ: Zelleetees/ eita augſcham"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee neins winnu Teltis/\nun gannamus Pulkus/ un wiſ-\nfus winnu Rihtus/ un atjems\npreektch teewim winnu Kameetus/\nun iſſanks prett winneem Bai-\nlibu wiſſapfahrt."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Behdseet/ atkahpeet\ntſchaſſli/apſlepjeetees dſittâs Wee-\ntâs/ juhs Gedſhwotaji no Azo-\nra/ fakka tas KUNGS: Jo\nNebukadRezars tas Rehninsch\nno Babeles irr weenu Padohmu\nprett jums fadohmajs/ un Doh-\nmas prett jums apdohmajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zelleetees/ eita augſcham\nprett teem Landim/ kam Meers\nirr/ kaſ drohſchi dſihwo/ fakka\ntas KUNGS: Kam neds Dur-\nwis/ neds Aisſchaujamce irr/tee\ndſihwo weeni paſchi."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winnu Kameeki buhs par\nLaupischanu/ un winnu ganna-\nmajs Pulks taps laupihts. Un\nees iſkaifischu tohs wiſſds Weh-\njôs/ kaſ pee tahkeem Stubreem\ndſihwo/ un es ativeddischu win-\nno Samaitaschanu no wiſſahn\nwinna Mallahm / fakka tas\nKUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Azors buhs par Puſ-\nku Mahjas-Weetu/ un pobſtâ\nmuhscham/ tur ne dſihwohs ne-\nweens/ neweeng Zilweka Behrus\nmittihs eekſch ta."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis irr ta KURSA\nWahrds/ kaſ notizzis irr uhs\nto Braueetu Jerenniju prett E-\nlannu / eeſch Gefahkuma tahs\nWat-"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
